"bereitgestellt."

#. Tag: para
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For an example of how to deploy Hibernate as a JMX service on the JBoss "
"Application Server, please see the JBoss User Guide. JBoss AS also provides "
"these benefits if you deploy using JMX:"
