msgstr ""
"Weitere Informationen zu diesen Optionen finden Sie im JBoss AS "
"Benutzerhandbuch."

#. Tag: para
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Another feature available as a JMX service is runtime Hibernate statistics. "
